        {
          "doc": "A direct-delivery (`swap_split_direct`) route's final step targeted a venue\\nthat can't pay a separate recipient \\xe2\\x80\\x94 Aquarius/Comet/Phoenix conflate the\\ninput source and output recipient, so they can only deliver to the router.",
          "name": "RecipientNotSupported",
          "value": 12
        },
        {
          "doc": "A route step referenced a token id that isn't in the registry (the\\nowner must `register_token` it first). A bad pool id is reported as\\n`TargetNotAllowed` (#5) \\xe2\\x80\\x94 the registry IS the swap-target allowlist.",
          "name": "TokenNotRegistered",
          "value": 13
        }
      ]
